## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="37a75-178">此属性只检索的替换字符串的项。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37a75-178">This property retrieves only the replacement strings for the entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="37a75-179">若要检索完整的消息，请参阅<xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogEntry.Message%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37a75-179">To retrieve the full message, read the <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogEntry.Message%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="37a75-180"><xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogEntry.ReplacementStrings%2A>属性包含在事件日志条目中使用的替换字符串的本地化的版本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37a75-180">The <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogEntry.ReplacementStrings%2A> property contains the localized versions of replacement strings that are used in the event log entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="37a75-181">如果你提供包含你的应用程序每种目标语言中的字符串的资源文件，您可以发出该计算机使用的语言中的事件日志消息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37a75-181">If you provide resource files that contain strings in each target language for your application, you can emit event log messages in the language that is used on that computer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="37a75-182">若要执行此操作，创建的实例<xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager>包含替换字符串的资源程序集的类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37a75-182">To do that, create an instance of the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager> class for the resource assembly that contains your replacement strings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="37a75-183">第一个参数<xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.Reflection.Assembly%29>构造函数标识要使用的资源程序集。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37a75-183">The first parameter of the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.Reflection.Assembly%29> constructor identifies the resource assembly to be used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="37a75-184">使用<xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager.GetString%2A>该实例提供日志事件的本地化的消息的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37a75-184">Use the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager.GetString%2A> method of that instance to supply localized messages for log events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="37a75-185">下面的代码自动设置为当前区域性的语言的消息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="37a75-185">The following code automatically sets the message to the language for the current culture.</span></span>  
  
```  
ResourceManager LocRM = new ResourceManager("ReplacementStrings.TestStrings",   
      typeof(Program).Assembly);  
EventLog e1 = new EventLog("LocTest", "MyMachine", "LocTest");  
// Get the string associated with the current culture.  
e1.WriteEntry(LocRM.GetString("strMessage"),  
   EventLogEntryType.Information);  
```
